                            <a> <img src="~/images/user/@girisYapanKullanici.ProfilePicture" class="img-thumbnail img-circle " style="height:40px;width:40px" />  &nbsp; @girisYapanKullanici.FirsName @girisYapanKullanici.LastName</a>
